g: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(135, 102, 58); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;董事长号召，公司上下要齐心协力，以主人翁的心态思考问题、解决问题，以合作谋发展，以发展图共赢，把小牛新财富带到一个新的高度。</strong></span></p></section></section></section></section><section class="" style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 100%; height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="float: left; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 1em; height: 1em; display: inline-block; border-top-right-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255);"></section><section style="display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 7px; height: 7px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; margin-bottom: -0.2em; margin-left: -0.2em; border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255);"></section><section style="width: 4px; height: 4px; margin-top: -0.3em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255);"></section></section></section><section style="float: right; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 4px; height: 4px; margin-top: -0.3em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255);"></section><section style="width: 7px; height: 7px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; margin-right: -0.2em; margin-bottom: -0.2em; border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255);"></section></section><section style="width: 1em; height: 1em; display: inline-block; border-top-left-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: